Package de.klassenserver7b.k7bot.logging

Enum Class LoggingOptions

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<LoggingOptions>
de.klassenserver7b.k7bot.logging.LoggingOptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<LoggingOptions>, Constable
public enum LoggingOptions extends Enum<LoggingOptions>
Enum representing every logging option which can be toggled by the logging config.
Used for guild specific logging selection.
Author:
Klassenserver7b
